#originalTopic=should-marriage-for-same-sex-couples-be-legal
for a long time now, i've been an advocate of gay marriage in every online community into which i set metaphorical foot.  i have seen the counter-arguments deployed against gay marriage countless times and i know that they have no legitimate basis, because they are not targeting gay marriage: they merely target gays.i find that particular detail telling.ed